OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776510170
OL,3,CStarmer to co-host talks on opening
OL,4,CStrait as Trump says war going
OL,5,C'swimmingly'
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer will say reopening
OL,8,Fthe Strait of Hormuz is a "global
OL,9,Fresponsibility" as he co-chairs a
OL,10,Fgathering of world leaders in Paris
OL,11,Fwith Emmanuel Macron on Friday.
OL,13,FThe Paris meeting is part of attempts
OL,14,Fby sidelined nations to ease the
OL,15,Fimpact of a conflict they didn't start
OL,16,Fand haven't joined, but that has sent
OL,17,Fthe global economy reeling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
