FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776510170
OL,3,CStarmer to co-host talks on opening
OL,4,CStrait as Trump says war going
OL,5,C'swimmingly'
OL,7,FThe Strait of Hormuz, a crucial
OL,8,Fshipping lane through which a fifth of
OL,9,Fthe world's oil normally flows, has
OL,10,Fbeen closed by Iran as a response to
OL,11,FAmerica and Israel's strikes.
OL,13,FIn retaliation, US President Donald
OL,14,FTrump begun his own blockade of Iran's
OL,15,Foil ports, aimed at cutting off
OL,16,FTehran's fossil fuel income.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776510170
OL,3,CStarmer to co-host talks on opening
OL,4,CStrait as Trump says war going
OL,5,C'swimmingly'
OL,7,FThe US is not part of the planning for
OL,8,Fwhat has been branded the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz Maritime Freedom of Navigation
OL,10,FInitiative, although around 40 other
OL,11,Fcountries, and the International
OL,12,FMaritime Organisation, are expected to
OL,13,Fbe on the call.
OL,15,FThe virtual summit will focus on
OL,16,Fsupporting the US-Iranian ceasefire
OL,17,Fand coming up with a plan to ensure
OL,18,Fthe Strait of Hormuz can remain open
OL,19,Fto shipping after the Middle East war
OL,20,Fends.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776510170
OL,3,CStarmer to co-host talks on opening
OL,4,CStrait as Trump says war going
OL,5,C'swimmingly'
OL,7,FIt comes as a 10-day ceasefire agreed
OL,8,Fby Lebanon and Israel that went into
OL,9,Feffect late on Thursday could boost
OL,10,Fattempts to extend the ceasefire
OL,11,Fbetween Iran, the US and Israel.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister is expected to tell
OL,14,Fthe summit: "The unconditional and
OL,15,Fimmediate reopening of the strait is a
OL,16,Fglobal responsibility, and we need to
OL,17,Fact to get global energy and trade
OL,18,Fflowing freely again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776510170
OL,3,CStarmer to co-host talks on opening
OL,4,CStrait as Trump says war going
OL,5,C'swimmingly'
OL,7,F"Emmanuel Macron and I are clear in
OL,8,Four commitment to establish a
OL,9,Fmultinational initiative to protect
OL,10,Ffreedom of navigation.
OL,12,F"We must reassure commercial shipping
OL,13,Fand support mine clearance operations
OL,14,Fto ensure a return to global stability
OL,15,Fand security."
OL,17,FStarmer will arrive in Paris late on
OL,18,FFriday morning to co-host the virtual
OL,19,Fmeeting with Mr Macron and then have
OL,20,Flunch with the French president.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
