OL,3,CStarmer to co-host talks on opening
OL,4,CStrait as Trump says war going
OL,5,C'swimmingly'
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper and
OL,13,FChief of the Defence Staff Sir Richard
OL,14,FKnighton will join the Prime Minister.
OL,16,FPlanning for a joint defensive mission
OL,17,Fis under way with a view to countries
OL,18,Fsending a combined military effort as
OL,19,Fsoon as conditions allow, Downing
OL,20,FStreet has said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
