PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776510170
OL,3,CStarmer to co-host talks on opening
OL,4,CStrait as Trump says war going
OL,5,C'swimmingly'
OL,7,FIn a post on X ahead of Friday's
OL,8,Fconference, French President Emmanuel
OL,9,FMacron said the mission to provide
OL,10,Fsecurity for shipping through the
OL,11,Fstrait would be "strictly defensive,"
OL,12,Flimited to non-belligerent countries
OL,13,Fand deployed "when security conditions
OL,14,Fallow."
OL,16,FThe conference on Friday will be
OL,17,Ffollowed up by a multinational
OL,18,Fmilitary planning summit at Permanent
OL,19,FJoint Headquarters in Northwood, north-
OL,20,Fwest London, next week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
