PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776510170
OL,3,CStarmer to co-host talks on opening
OL,4,CStrait as Trump says war going
OL,5,C'swimmingly'
OL,7,FIt comes as Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,8,Fhas been speaking out about her
OL,9,Ffrustration at the "folly" of
OL,10,FAmerica's offensive and its financial
OL,11,Ffallout on families.
OL,13,FDuring a trip to Washington this week,
OL,14,Fthe Chancellor said a "swift and
OL,15,Flasting" end to the conflict was the
OL,16,Fbest way to get prices down for the UK
OL,17,Fpublic and insisted she is continuing
OL,18,Fto work "very constructively" with the
OL,19,FUS administration.
OL,26,@qD@TOUqD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
