PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776510170
OL,3,CStarmer to co-host talks on opening
OL,4,CStrait as Trump says war going
OL,5,C'swimmingly'
OL,7,FThe Foreign Secretary is on her own
OL,8,Fdiplomatic offensive in run-up to the
OL,9,FUS-Iran ceasefire expiring on Tuesday
OL,10,Fand is due to visit Turkey and the
OL,11,FGulf as well as Japan.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, President Donald Trump has
OL,14,Ftold reporters that the war in Iran is
OL,15,F"going along swimmingly", saying that
OL,16,Fit "should be ending pretty soon".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
