OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776510170
OL,3,CStarmer to co-host talks on opening
OL,4,CStrait as Trump says war going
OL,5,C'swimmingly'
OL,7,FSpeaking in Las Vegas speech, the US
OL,8,FPresident said he was feeling pretty
OL,9,Fpositive about the Iran war, despite
OL,10,Fthe energy price spikes, the death and
OL,11,Fdestruction and the anxiety about the
OL,12,Ffuture of NATO and the Middle East.
OL,14,FTrump added that the war was "was
OL,15,Fperfect" as he praised the power of
OL,16,Fthe US military.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
